Package: vibeCheck
Type: Package
Title: Interactive R Package Documentation Assistant
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Li", "Richard Zehang", email = "lizehang@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: An interactive Shiny application for analyzing R package documentation,
    dependencies, and generating roxygen2 documentation templates. Provides comprehensive dependency analysis, missing package detection, and smart parameter suggestions based on existing documentation patterns. The package is created with vibe coding using Claude.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/richardli/vibeCheck
BugReports: https://github.com/richardli/vibeCheck/issues
